translation.Go into raid with only a Mosin. No armor: Go into raid with only a Mosin. No armor, no backpack, and no meds. Only Mosin comrade.
translation.Take in any gear you want but you can on: Take in any gear you want but you can only crawl the entire raid
translation.Go into raid with your absolute most exp: Go into raid with your absolute most expensive gear. Strike fear into the hearts of all who cross your path and leave no survivors. Rush all engagements and take no prisoners
translation.Go into raid with nothing. Pick up nothi: Go into raid with nothing. Pick up nothing. Extract with nothing. If you can complete this task, you are a god

translation.Go into raid with whatever you like but: Go into raid with whatever you like but your first kill must be with a melee weapon
translation.Go into raid with full UN armor. Find an: Go into raid with full UN armor. Find an enemy and make peace with them over VOIP
translation.Successfully complete an interview with: Successfully complete an interview with another player over VOIP
translation.Go into raid with a squad and make a con: Go into raid with a squad and make a conga line. Wiggling required. See how many strangers you can get to join the party!
translation.Aquire a Santa bag. Fill it up with pres: Aquire a Santa bag. Fill it up with presents. Go into raid and give out gifts!
translation.Aquire as many green smoke grenades as y: Aquire as many green smoke grenades as you can fit in your inventory. Go into Factory, sit in office, and fill the entire room with green smoke. Bonus points for blasting Snoop Dogg over VOIP
Double barrel shotgun and a cowboy hat. Optionally swap the shotgun for the revolver. Yee Haw!
